snippet.title: ESF: Final - Almost endless Flying
snippet.description:
Video is part of: "YES.. WE ARE STILL ALIVE  NEWS!" at:  https://forum.esforces.com/threads/yes-we-are-still-alive.158687

This video will show you portion of the actual map size by going through the border (which by default you normally can't go through), you can fly/walk/swim almost indefinitely. Though for the purpose of that video, only a small portion is shown.It takes about 21 seconds to get from point A to point B with turbo.
